                                            ^
Recursive dependencies detected when resolving function simple_module.bar, which include objects (simple_module.bar, simple_module.baz, simple_module.foo, simple_module.bar) [at 3:25]

Lazy_resolution_function:foo
ERROR: Function foo is invalid [at 2:24]
CREATE PUBLIC FUNCTION foo(d int64) as (1 + bar(d));
                       ^
